<item>
            <title>[FLINK-1154] YarnTaskManagerRunner does not shut down</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1154</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The YarnClient does not shut down the YarnTaskManagerRunner when the client receives a stop command or is terminated. This causes a resource leak on the cluster.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12747519">FLINK-1154</key>
            <summary>YarnTaskManagerRunner does not shut down</summary>
